Package it.polimi.ingsw.network

Interface IClientListener

All Superinterfaces:
Remote, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
ClientListenerGUI, ClientListenerTUI, ServerSocketClientHandler
public interface IClientListener extends Remote, Serializable
this interface's methods are called mainly by the server to communicate with the client via RMI (using ClientListenerGUI and ClientListenerTUI) or via Socket (using ServerSocketClientHandler)
